193
00:16:33,296 --> 00:16:34,296
Tak.

194
00:16:36,296 --> 00:16:38,296
Nie wiem. Myślę.

195
00:16:44,858 --> 00:16:46,858
Dzisiaj?

196
00:16:50,858 --> 00:16:52,858
Dobrze.

197
00:16:52,858 --> 00:16:56,858
